_xResult.title: Yes Ma'am Jacket
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made cashmere jacket with two side pockets
_xResult.longdesc:
Defy odds in this custom made winter coat. Made of intoxicatingly soft and premium cashmere, this jacket features two side pockets with buttons, pleats on the front bodice, long-sleeves and an asymmetrical cut that flows into a long midi-length hemline. Snag this coat as a stand-out piece for your winter collection—no one will have anything like it!
